{
  "id": "guide/i18n-common-add-package",
  "title": "Add the localize package",
  "contents": "\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-add-package.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"add-the-localize-package\" translation-result=\"on\">添加本地化包<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package#add-the-localize-package\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"add-the-localize-package\">Add the localize package<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-add-package#add-the-localize-package\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<a id=\"setting-up-cli\"></a>\n<a id=\"add-localize\"></a>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要利用 Angular 的本地化功能，请用 Angular CLI 将 <code>@angular/localize</code> 包添加到你的项目中。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To take advantage of the localization features of Angular, use the Angular CLI to add the <code>@angular/localize</code> package to your project.</p>\n\n<code-example path=\"i18n/doc-files/commands.sh\" region=\"add-localize\" language=\"sh\">\nng add @angular/localize\n\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">此命令会更新项目的 <code>package.json</code> 和 <code>polyfills.ts</code> 文件以导入 <code>@angular/localize</code> 包。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">This command updates the <code>package.json</code> and <code>polyfills.ts</code> files of your project to import the <code>@angular/localize</code> package.</p>\n\n<div class=\"alert is-helpful\">\n<p translation-result=\"on\">有关 <code>package.json</code> 和 polyfill 包的更多信息，请参阅<a href=\"guide/npm-packages\" title=\"Workspace npm dependencies | Angular\">工作区的 npm 依赖项</a>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">For more information about <code>package.json</code> and polyfill packages, see <a href=\"guide/npm-packages\" title=\"Workspace npm dependencies | Angular\">Workspace npm dependencies</a>.</p>\n\n</div>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">如果未安装 <code>@angular/localize</code> ，当你尝试构建应用程序的本地化版本时，Angular CLI 可能会产生错误。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">If <code>@angular/localize</code> is not installed, the Angular CLI may generate an error when you try to build a localized version of your application.</p>\n\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间： 2021/9/15</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - guide/i18n-common\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - guide/i18n-common-add-package#add-the-localize-package\n - guide/npm-packages\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-add-package.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n-->"
}